) (

). In addition, the molecular docking results coincided with the kinetic analysis in vitro, which revealed that compound 
370
has high binding affinity with the targets of AChE and BACE1, and therefore it is an effective AChE and BACE1 inhibitors. In addition, the studies of flavonoids as lead compounds for the treatment of AD reported the activities of a series of prenylated flavonoids (
